uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model

Class CValue<V extends IValue>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.CValue<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEntity
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CDataValue, CFrame, MFrame

    public abstract class CValue<V extends IValue>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FEntity
    Represents an entity that can act as the value-type for an instance-level slot. Value-type-entities can be either concept-level or meta-level (since the value-entities they define can be either instance-level or concept-level).
